This version of the MedievalTown application is only compatible with inVRs 
v1.0alpha3 or maybe higher!

For more information please visit: http://www.invrs.org

USAGE:

Final application:
Keyb.: W ................. move forward
Keyb.: S ................. move backward
Keyb.: A ................. strafe left
Keyb.: D ................. strafe right
Keyb.: M ................. toggle cursor fixed/released in window

Mouse: left/right ........ turn left/right
Mouse: up/down ........... look upward/downward
Mouse: MMB + left/right .. rotate camera (roll)
Mouse: LMB ............... pick up entity (when selected)
                           release entity (when picked up)
Mouse: RMB ............... windmill animation

